  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A person who sneaked into the parliament is caught",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A suspected woman who tried to trespass to the Parliament was arrested by the officers of the Jayantipura main police post today (2) in the morning.",
        "A police official said that the question is why the woman tried to enter the parliament and they are continuing to question her in that regard.",
        "This woman tried to enter Jayanthipura from the main entrance in a panic yesterday morning. At this time, the police officers who were there prevented her from entering and a policewoman was deployed and took the woman aside and proceeded to arrest her.",
        "The suspect woman was then handed over to Thalangama police for further investigations."
      ],
